# Summary
Ask Amplitude is a conversational interface that allows users to create charts, search content, answer questions, navigate Amplitude, and create shareable threads using natural language. It leverages OpenAI's LLM to understand requests and generate responses, sending chart metadata, taxonomy information, dashboard names, and aggregated results to the OpenAI API.

